1
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:14,840
You, over here.

2
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:17,960
So many flowers bloomed overnight.

3
00:00:18,080 --> 00:00:18,680
Over here.

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:20,520
Be careful.

5
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:22,680
Not a single flower is allowed in the Master's mansion.

6
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:24,520
Come with me to the backyard first.

7
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:26,180
Last year we missed that spot,

8
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,800
and the Master saw it by chance.

9
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:31,320
That manager was thrown directly into the private dungeon by the Master.

10
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:32,980
I heard she lost half her life.

11
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:35,680
I don't want to follow in her footsteps.

12
00:00:35,680 --> 00:00:36,160
You,

13
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:36,760
take

14
00:00:37,560 --> 00:00:38,760
the flowers.

15
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:50,760
Come and listen.

16
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,220
Are they turning the soil?

17
00:00:54,040 --> 00:00:55,840
I heard the Lady of Huifeng Hall

18
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:57,280
used to be a flower slave.

19
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,720
Oh, my lady.

20
00:01:00,720 --> 00:01:03,480
Flowers are forbidden in the Master's mansion.

21
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:05,090
If the Master finds out,

22
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:07,800
you and all of us will die a graveless death.

23
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:09,880
My lady.

24
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:14,520
You, get some people to break the door open.

25
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:16,760
What's hanging on the door is from your Master's study,

26
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,360
the most expensive jade ruyi.

27
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:20,960
Smash it if you're not afraid of being punished.

28
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:21,840
You stay here and watch.

29
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,170
I'll go find the Master.

30
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:25,280
Master.

31
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,760
The servants said

32
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:29,039
Lady Fang brought flowers to the backyard.

33
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:31,680
Yes, Master, please do something.

34
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:34,240
Lady Fang is planting flowers in the backyard.

35
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:35,080
Lady Fang.

36
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:37,759
She even blocked it with your jade ruyi.

37
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,560
We didn't dare to smash it.

38
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:40,250
Smash it.

39
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,020
Move aside.

40
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,720
Drag Lady Fang out

41
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:51,380
and lock her up.

42
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,259
Somebody come.

43
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:58,759
Bring a torch.

44
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:01,760
Master, please see clearly.

45
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,440
These flowers,

46
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:05,040
I planted them as a birthday gift for my mother.

47
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,720
It is out of my filial piety,

48
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,449
and also for your sake, Master.

49
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,220
Do you know that in my mansion,

50
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,240
planting flowers is a taboo?

51
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,560
I am new here,

52
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,880
how would I know about any taboos?

53
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:16,760
If I had known,

54
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,880
even if I were given a hundred times the courage,

55
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,320
I would never dare.

56
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,560
Master, please see clearly.

57
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,960
I did try to stop Lady Fang just now.

58
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,920
The head maid did say something.

59
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,760
But it was too late,

60
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,690
I had already planted the flowers.

61
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:36,480
Now I'm afraid the whole Kuizhou City knows

62
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,640
that I will present rare flowers to my mother.

63
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,160
If I cannot deliver them when the time comes,

64
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:43,000
and implicate the whole mansion,

65
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:46,730
I wouldn't be able to absolve myself even with ten thousand deaths.

66
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,329
Are you threatening me?

67
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,200
I don't believe a single word

68
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,200
you say.

69
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,360
Take her away.

70
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,500
Everything I said is true.

71
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,640
Even if you insist on executing me,

72
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,320
I will let

73
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,760
everyone in Kuizhou know

74
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,360
that I planted flowers for my mother

75
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,400
and died for my filial piety.

76
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:22,079
I heard the Commander was furious last night.

77
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,720
He was so angry he even overturned his medicine bowl.

78
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:27,400
Saying that the Third Young Master was acting recklessly out of favor,

79
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:31,060
not only did he take a low-status woman into the mansion on his own,

80
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:34,000
but he also caused chaos in his own household,

81
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:38,100
making the entire Kuizhou watch the Governor's Mansion as a joke.

82
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:41,680
The Third Young Master kneeled at the door of the study all night

83
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,760
and just went back.

84
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:45,880
My son,

85
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,160
he really is a romantic.

86
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,440
First it was that Lady Ye,

87
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,079
and now,

88
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,040
it's Fang Qingcheng.

89
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,760
The Third Young Master has had a leg ailment for a long time.

90
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,800
His official career has long been hopeless.

91
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,000
As a crippled person,

92
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,840
doesn't he only have some little desires left?

93
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:06,920
The Master didn't say anything else besides this.

94
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:09,000
Rest assured, Madam.

95
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,780
The Governor hasn't blamed you even half a word.

96
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:16,600
It was his own decision to let that flower slave into the mansion.

97
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,600
If he can't manage his own people

98
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,120
and the trouble reaches the Master,

99
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:22,120
it's not something I can control.

100
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:25,560
Everyone knows I dote on my son.

101
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:28,280
Don't I accommodate him in everything?

102
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:31,480
You are right, Madam. Not to mention this matter

103
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,000
has nothing to do with you,

104
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,170
even if it really had some connection,

105
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,440
over these years,

106
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,920
in which matter

107
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,640
has the Governor not followed your wishes?

108
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,920
The affection between the Master and me

109
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,120
is not something others can compare to.

110
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:50,280
Prepare some ointment to promote blood circulation and relieve stasis,

111
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:52,600
and send it to the Young Master's mansion.

112
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,480
Our Third Young Master's knees

113
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,000
can't take any more torment.

114
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,760
Yes.

115
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,160
As usual.

116
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,560
Rest assured, Madam.

117
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:08,210
Your affection for the Third Young Master

118
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:12,360
will be seen by everyone.

119
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,900
This thing about flowers,

120
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:21,320
you just have to trim it more for it to be to your liking.

121
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,240
Tell me,

122
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,320
for my birthday banquet,

123
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:28,080
he definitely won't bring that flower slave,

124
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:28,680
right?

125
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,400
It doesn't conform to etiquette,

126
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:33,860
not to mention the Third Young Master hates her to the bone now.

127
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,960
Pass on the word

128
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,040
to let her come.

129
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,880
Yes.

130
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,840
My lady,

131
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:54,480
do you know what is special about my water dungeon?

132
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,680
Ordinary water dungeons

133
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,200
take lives

134
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,800
using water.

135
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,360
But here,

136
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,240
I rely on fire.

137
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,960
Lady,

138
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,040
do you feel anything?

139
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,080
Please see clearly, my lord.

140
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,600
My devotion to you

141
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,520
is sincere.

142
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:21,360
I'm afraid there must be some misunderstanding in this.

143
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,880
I have a few questions,

144
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,400
and I hope you can

145
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:27,320
answer them truthfully.

146
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,480
Just ask, my lord.

147
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,520
I will certainly tell you everything I know.

148
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:32,440
At Wei hour the day before the wedding,

149
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,480
where were you?

150
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:36,560
I

151
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,560
was resting in my own room.

152
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,560
You're lying.

153
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,080
Maybe you forgot,

154
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,000
let me kindly remind you.

155
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:48,640
There was a woodcutter.

156
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:52,240
I saw you at the back mountain this afternoon.

157
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,170
My cousin went missing,

158
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,640
so I went to the back mountain to look for her.

159
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,480
If so,

160
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,120
why did you lie?

161
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,080
At a time like this,

162
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:08,920
if I admitted going to the back mountain,

163
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,290
wouldn't it arouse suspicion?

164
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,340
I didn't want any trouble,

165
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,210
so I never mentioned it.

166
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,320
Why did you go to the back mountain?

167
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,120
I...

168
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,880
realized

169
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,720
my cousin forgot her bamboo hook.

170
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,760
I went to look for her,

171
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,820
but couldn't find her,

172
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,400
so I came down.

173
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,780
Do you have any witnesses?

174
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,880
If you don't tell the truth,

175
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:51,920
it seems the water temperature needs to be raised.

176
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:55,800
Wait.

177
00:07:56,960 --> 00:08:00,280
Every word I said is true.

178
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,480
My husband,

179
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:04,370
what will it take for you to believe me?

180
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,400
You two sisters,

181
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:06,520
one is an impostor,

182
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,560
and one mysteriously missing,

183
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,880
and now you both went to the back mountain.

184
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,360
One thing leads to another.

185
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,720
What is your intention?

186
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,520
I've said all I should.

187
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,490
If you insist on killing me,

188
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,120
I guarantee

189
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,320
that you will never

190
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,420
see Qingcheng again in your life.

191
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,560
Then I will kill her beloved sister.

192
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,440
I just want to see

193
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,200
if she will show up.

194
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:41,409
Do you still not want to tell the truth?

195
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:46,880
You

196
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:50,080
say I harbor ulterior motives.

197
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,240
But I think you

198
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,960
are not any nobler.

199
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:58,530
You, the Third Master of the Governor's Mansion,

200
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:01,980
are willing to marry a merchant's daughter.

201
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,080
Isn't it just for money?

202
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,880
How about

203
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,240
you let me go,

204
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:11,290
and the dividends of Yanzhi Pavilion,

205
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:13,360
I'll share with you?

206
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,520
What do you think?

207
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:20,120
A mere flower slave,

208
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,760
how dare you speak so arrogantly!

209
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:22,240
Tell me,

210
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,220
where did you hide Qingcheng?

211
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,440
Or

212
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,400
did you kill her

213
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,060
to take over Yanzhi Pavilion?

214
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,040
Young Master.

215
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:34,840
Madam suddenly sent word,

216
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,920
asking Lady Fang to enter the Governor's Mansion the day after tomorrow,

217
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:39,180
to attend the birthday banquet with you.

218
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,120
Men,

219
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,960
let Lady Fang down.

220
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,640
Young Master.

221
00:09:57,720 --> 00:10:00,680
Do you really think Lady Fang works for Madam?

222
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,560
Madam Li's message

223
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:04,520
came a bit too coincidentally.

224
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,200
Since she came to my mansion,

225
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:09,500
she has been against me at every turn.

226
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,520
A mere flower slave

227
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,280
keeps saying

228
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:17,240
she wants to share the prosperity of Yanzhi Pavilion with me.

229
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,560
Such arrogance,

230
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,050
she must have someone backing her.

231
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,200
The one in Qiwu Courtyard

232
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:31,040
has been using this method to contact the hidden agents.

233
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:31,480
Go

234
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,280
and find a way

235
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:35,440
to put this in Fang Zhuozhuo's room.

236
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:40,480
What if Lady Fang really goes to Qiwu Courtyard

237
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,880
and meets with the Madam?

238
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,960
To save Xin'er,

239
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,600
then we definitely can't let her live.

